rows.label: tlk42300021_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Coming to Gula might have been
a mistake... mo.

rows.label: tlk42300021_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Shatoto came from Avaritia to
do business in this country, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300021_01_msg0003
rows.name:
But selling Shatoto's goods in this city
only earned me pennies, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300021_01_msg0004
rows.name:
It reminds me of what my mother
used to say, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300021_01_msg0006
rows.name:
For the Gulan and Superbian people in Torigo,
Shatoto's goods aren't appealing... mo.

rows.label: tlk42300021_01_msg0008
rows.name:
But I don't have the money to return to
Avaritia, so I'm in a bind, mo.
